item.title: Sample Page
item.dc:creator: StephanieH
item.content:encoded:
This is an example page. It's different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:
Hi there! I'm a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like piña coladas. (And gettin' caught in the rain.)
...or something like this:
The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.
As a new WordPress user, you should go to your dashboard to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!

item.title: Theme features
item.dc:creator: StephanieH
item.content:encoded:
The home page options for our Elegance theme are really only limited by your imagination!

You can completely change the look of your homepage by simply rearranging widgets in the available widget areas. Here are a few different ways to style your homepage to give you a few ideas:

Not into the black and white look to frame your photography or artwork?

No problem! Elegance is highly customizable. Built right into the WordPress customizer you can change the colors without knowing or editing any code! You have control over the look and feel of your site with the ability to edit the main color, the accent color and various text colors and links. Built right into the Customizer color options are a nice selection of specific elements you can change and previewlive! No more saving options and refreshing the live site just to see what it might look like. You can make your edits, view the changes live then save and publish your custom options when ready! You are in control of the annoucement bar and footer background color, accent color, link color, body text and more.

Built to save you time and confusion.

When we sit down and create a theme, design is not our only focus. We want to also deliver a product that can save you time and make installation as simple as possible - even for folks who are new to the whole process. Included in our themes is a feature that prompts you to install all the plugins necessary to set up your theme as you see in our demo. It is as simple as a click of a button! No more searching for a plugin and installing and then activating one by one. You are going to love our plugin installer!

Elegance is styled for the Genesis Portfolio Pro plugin!

The Genesis Portfolio Pro plugin allows you to build a portfolio that you don't lose when you decide to update or switch themes. Elegance has special styling for the Genesis Portfolio Pro plugin to frame your best work! View the demo here.
BUY NOW

Want to utilize your website for more than just a portfolio site?

Elegance is styled to work with a free plugin that allows you to upload private client galleries and offers your customers the ability to select their favorite shots. This provides a nice workflow for narrowing down images into a curated group of images for your clients to purchase.  

Elegance has the following built-in page templates:

  • Archive Page
  • Category Archive Page
  • Blog Page
  • Portfolio Page
  • Proof Gallery
  • and a styled Pricing Table
BUY NOW

item.dc:creator: StephanieH
item.content:encoded:
This is a demonstration of how you can use the PixProof plugin to allow your customers to communicate their choice of images from a photo shoot.
While Elegance is styled for the pixproof plugin, there are other premium plugins that also allow this functionality that you may enjoy working with. I recommend setting a password for the client gallery and then sending your customer the urlto their private gallery with the password.
You can offer some instructions, comments or important information for your clients here.
